"   Dextroamphetamine: Drug information",
"  </div>",
"  <div id=\"lexiTitleImg\">",
"   <img height=\"17\" src=\"./../images/lexiComp/Lexicomp_2012_71x17.myextg\" width=\"71\"/>",
"  </div>",
"  <div class=\"clear\">",
"  </div>",
"  <div id=\"drugCopy\">",
"   Copyright 1978-2013 Lexicomp, Inc. All rights reserved.",
"  </div>",
"  <div id=\"topicText\">",
"   (For additional information",
"   <a class=\"drug drug_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?28/15/28917?source=see_link\">",
